Usage: checkTimingLibrary [-help] [-cellname <string>] [-checkpower]
                          [-library <string>] [-outfile <string>]
                          [-reportMissingPowerOnly]

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
-cellname <string>          # Specify the cell name. (string, optional)
-checkpower                 # Checks if power constructs are defined for the
                            # cells, such as internal_power, leakage_power, or
                            # ecsm_power. (bool, optional)
-library <string>           # Specify the library name. (string, optional)
-outfile <string>           # Output File Name (string, optional)
-reportMissingPowerOnly     # Reports only the cells that do not have
                            # internal_power (at pin level), or leakage_power
                            # defined. (bool, optional)